The paper focuses on the usability of secure email systems, which involves both human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and computer security (cs.CR). The study also touches on issues related to privacy and cryptography (cs.CY), as well as software engineering (cs.SE) in terms of designing and implementing secure email systems. Finally, the study involves the use of technology to facilitate communication (cs.SI).
